# Benchmark artifacts. The compiled bench binary is not portable across
# machines, and the generated CSVs / PDFs are expected to come from CI
# rather than from whichever laptop happened to run them. Anything
# checked-in by hand can be force-added with `git add -f`.
*_bench/bench
*_bench/results.csv
*_bench/*.pdf

# Test binaries.
*_tests/tests
